  "detailed_description": "A both intense and relaxing particle simulation for VR. Experience hundreds of thousands of seemingly living particles.<br>Use VR controllers to interact with different particle systems, or create your own using the editor. For Vive and Oculus Rift.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/fdfb66ce2659f02ab4ec518a755a29e2.poster.avif?t=1516214087\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/fdfb66ce2659f02ab4ec518a755a29e2.webm?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/fdfb66ce2659f02ab4ec518a755a29e2.mp4?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience up to 250,000 particles with physics.<br></li><li> Emit, interact with the particles and control time, using your VR controllers.<br></li><li> Create your own scenes with the in-game editor.<br></li><li> Change 3d models, skies, lights, materials, emitters.<br></li><li> Export Gif animations and screenshots.</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/851112eb8a8535db7d31ef844049f649.poster.avif?t=1516214087\" width=560 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/851112eb8a8535db7d31ef844049f649.webm?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/851112eb8a8535db7d31ef844049f649.mp4?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/19def2aec4142d7070a46cb27cebbfd2.poster.avif?t=1516214087\" width=552 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/19def2aec4142d7070a46cb27cebbfd2.webm?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612840/extras/19def2aec4142d7070a46cb27cebbfd2.mp4?t=1516214087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
